  "name": "Overload Magic",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-green.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> to channel raw magical energy for 1 minute, or until you become Incapacitated, die, or choose to end it early at any time (0 <strong>AP</strong>).</p>\n<p>For the duration, your magic is overloaded and you are subjected to the following effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain +5 to all Spell Checks you make.</li>\n<li>You must make a DC 10 <strong>Mental Save </strong>as soon as you&nbsp;overload your magic. You must repeat this Save at the start&nbsp;of each of your subsequent turns. <br><strong>Failure:</strong> You take True&nbsp;damage equal to the number of rounds your magic has been&nbsp;overloaded since the start of Combat.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Mana Afterburn</strong></span></p>\n<p>When the effect ends, you must spend an amount of <strong>MP </strong>equal<br>to your Combat Mastery or gain <strong>Exhaustion 1</strong> (your choice).</p>",
